	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64173199"><p>You'd need to identify and prove beyond a reasonable doubt that <br>
<span class="substr"> </span> <br>1. that particular game asset was AI generated, and<br>
 <br>2. the asset had not been modified in <i>any way</i> after generation, since modifying the asset makes it an original work and thus copyrightable<br>
 <br>There's an extremely thin slice of AI generated work, like chat responses, first pass image generation that doesn't have copyright, but also has zero or close to zero economic value. You don't get to pirate the entire game GTA VI simpl</p></div>
